        <div class="statement col-md-9  content-container " id='contribution-cef6a79c-d16f-4522-93d0-c3ac69b03a68'>
            
<p class="">Question put accordingly:</p><p class=""> <blockquote><q>"That the Control of Motor Fuel Order, 1947 (S.R. &amp; O., 1947, No. 2058), dated 22nd September, 1947, a copy of which was presented on 20th October, be annulled."</q></blockquote></p>
