, D. E. (Aberdare)</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Crawley, A.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Macpherson, T. (Romford)</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Thomas, J. O. (Wrekin)</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Daggar, G.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Mallalieu, J. P. W.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Thomas, George (Cardiff)</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Davies, Edward (Burslem)</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Mann, Mrs. J.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Thorneycroft. Harry (Clayton)</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Deer, G.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Mathers, Rt. Hon. G</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Tiffany, S.</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>de Freilas, Geoffrey</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Medland, H. M.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Timmons, J.</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Delargy, H. J</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Mellish, R. J.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Tomlinson, Rt. Hon. G</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Diamond, J.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Middleton, Mrs. L.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Walker, G. H</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Dobbie, W.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Mikardo, Ian.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Wallace, G. D. (Chislehurst)</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Dye, S.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Millington, Wing-Comdr E R</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Watkins, T. E.</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p